<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Formations Pro - Achat en ligne</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Montserrat:wght@700&family=Poppins:wght@500&family=Roboto&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        body { font-family: 'Roboto', sans-serif; margin: 0; padding: 0; background-color: #f4f6f8; color: #333; }
        header { background-color: #1f4068; color: white; padding: 30px 0; text-align: center; }
        header h1 { font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif; margin: 0; }
        nav { display: flex; justify-content: center; background-color: #162447; font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif; }
        nav a { color: white; padding: 14px 20px; text-decoration: none; text-transform: uppercase; }
        nav a:hover { background-color: #1f4068; }
        section { padding: 50px; text-align: center; }
        h2 { font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif; margin-bottom: 30px; }
        .formations { display: flex; justify-content: center; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 30px; }
        .formation-card { background-color: white; border-radius: 10px; box-shadow: 0 6px 12px rgba(0,0,0,0.1); padding: 20px; width: 300px; transition: transform 0.3s, box-shadow 0.3s; text-align: left; }
        .formation-card:hover { transform: translateY(-5px); box-shadow: 0 10px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.2); }
        .formation-card h3 { font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif; margin-top: 0; }
        .formation-card p { font-size: 14px; color: #555; }
        .formation-card ul { padding-left: 20px; margin: 10px 0; }
        .formation-card form button { margin-top: 15px; padding: 10px 20px; border: none; border-radius: 5px; background-color: #1f4068; color: white; cursor: pointer; font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif; transition: background 0.3s; }
        .formation-card form button:hover { background-color: #162447; }
        .testimonials { background-color: #0d1b2a; color: white; padding: 50px 20px; }
        .testimonial { max-width: 500px; margin: 20px auto; font-style: italic; }
        footer { background-color: #162447; color: white; padding: 30px 20px; text-align: center; }
        input, textarea { padding: 10px; width: 80%; max-width: 400px; border-radius: 5px; border: 1px solid #ccc; margin-bottom: 15px; }
        button.newsletter-btn { padding: 10px 20px; background-color: #1f4068; color: white; border: none; border-radius: 5px; cursor: pointer; }
        button.newsletter-btn:hover { background-color: #162447; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

<header>
    <h1>Formations Pro</h1>
    <p>Boostez votre carrière avec nos formations en ligne</p>
</header>

<nav>
    <a href="#formations">Formations</a>
    <a href="#temoignages">Témoignages</a>
    <a href="#contact">Contact</a>
</nav>

<section id="formations">
    <h2>Nos Formations</h2>
    <div class="formations">

        <!-- HTML/CSS -->
        <div class="formation-card">
            <h3>HTML/CSS Complète</h3>
            <p>Créez des sites web modernes, responsives et professionnels.</p>
            <ul>
                <li>10 modules du niveau débutant au avancé</li>
                <li>Exercices pratiques pour chaque module</li>
                <li>Modèles de sites personnalisables</li>
                <li>Support en ligne pour toutes vos questions</li>
                <li>Certificat de fin de formation</li>
            </ul>
            <p><strong>Prix : 49€</strong></p>
            <form action="https://www.paypal.com/cgi-bin/webscr" method="post" target="_blank">
                <input type="hidden" name="cmd" value="_xclick">
                <input type="hidden" name="business" value="ton-email-paypal@example.com">
                <input type="hidden" name="item_name" value="Formation HTML/CSS Complète">
                <input type="hidden" name="amount" value="49.00">
                <input type="hidden" name="currency_code" value="EUR">
                <input type="hidden" name="return" value="contenu-html-css.html">
                <button type="submit">Acheter</button>
            </form>
        </div>

        <!-- JavaScript -->
        <div class="formation-card">
            <h3>JavaScript</h3>
            <p>Créez des sites interactifs et dynamiques.</p>
            <p><strong>Prix : 69€</strong></p>
            <form action="https://www.paypal.com/cgi-bin/webscr" method="post" target="_blank">
                <input type="hidden" name="cmd" value="_xclick">
                <input type="hidden" name="business" value="ton-email-paypal@example.com">
                <input type="hidden" name="item_name" value="Formation JavaScript">
                <input type="hidden" name="amount" value="69.00">
                <input type="hidden" name="currency_code" value="EUR">
                <input type="hidden" name="return" value="contenu-js.html">
                <button type="submit">Acheter</button>
            </form>
        </div>

        <!-- React -->
        <div class="formation-card">
            <h3>React</h3>
            <p>Créez des applications web modernes avec React.</p>
            <p><strong>Prix : 99€</strong></p>
            <form action="https://www.paypal.com/cgi-bin/webscr" method="post" target="_blank">
                <input type="hidden" name="cmd" value="_xclick">
                <input type="hidden" name="business" value="ton-email-paypal@example.com">
                <input type="hidden" name="item_name" value="Formation React">
                <input type="hidden" name="amount" value="99.00">
                <input type="hidden" name="currency_code" value="EUR">
                <input type="hidden" name="return" value="contenu-react.html">
                <button type="submit">Acheter</button>
            </form>
        </div>

    </div>
</section>

<section id="temoignages" class="testimonials">
    <h2>Témoignages</h2>
    <div class="testimonial">"Ces formations ont changé ma vie ! Merci pour votre pédagogie." – Alice</div>
    <div class="testimonial">"J’ai trouvé un emploi grâce à ces cours." – Julien</div>
    <div class="testimonial">"Contenu clair, exercices pratiques, je recommande !" – Sophie</div>
</section>

<section id="contact">
    <h2>Contact / Newsletter</h2>
    <p>Inscrivez-vous pour recevoir nos offres et nouveautés :</p>
    <form onsubmit="newsletter(event)">
        <input type="text" placeholder="Nom" required><br>
        <input type="email" placeholder="Email" required><br>
        <button type="submit" class="newsletter-btn">S’inscrire</button>
    </form>
</section>

<footer>
    <p>© 2026 Formations Pro – Tous droits réservés</p>
</footer>

<script>
    function newsletter(event) {
        event.preventDefault();
        alert('Merci pour votre inscription ! Vous recevrez nos offres par email.');
    }
</script>

</body>
</html>
